profile:
General Concrete LTD. is a full service concrete and construction contractor.  Concrete Breaking, disposal, forming walls, retaining walls and driveways, land prep, bobcat and hoe work.  All types of finishes in stamp concrete, broom finish, smooth floors, concrete patios and concrete driveways.  

We also have winter maintenance in snow removal and liquid salting.
services:
Concrete retaining walls, stamp patios and driveways, broom finish, exposed finish, concrete breaking, land prep, forming of all types.  Flat works and retaining walls.

Bobcat work, trenching, drainage, and demo in concrete and buildings.
